01:16:21.000 --> 01:16:30.000
So we get in the car and they take me down into the jail and pull through the process.

01:16:30.000 --> 01:16:31.000
And I remember that night.

01:16:31.000 --> 01:16:33.000
I had enough sense to keep my clothes on.

01:16:33.000 --> 01:16:35.000
They put me in solitary.

01:16:35.000 --> 01:16:42.000
So I've been solitary.

01:16:42.000 --> 01:16:44.000
It was light on my face.

01:16:44.000 --> 01:16:46.000
It's black.

01:16:46.000 --> 01:16:53.000
And I hear a voice, a disembodied voice saying, I'm not in the clan.

