01:17:08.000 --> 01:17:10.000
I'm not in the clan, but I'm awake.

01:17:10.000 --> 01:17:13.000
And I was sitting up.

01:17:13.000 --> 01:17:17.000
I looked at me, sort of, rucked and looking at a nice tight crew cut.

01:17:17.000 --> 01:17:19.000
I'm not in the clan.

