01:18:39.000 --> 01:18:44.000
Man, he's blind, completely blind, since apparently, since childhood.

01:18:44.000 --> 01:18:50.000
And was raised as a very strong, talismage faction part of Georgia politics.

01:18:50.000 --> 01:18:53.000
