01:21:24.000 --> 01:21:26.000
We couldn't see so and so forth.

01:21:26.000 --> 01:21:29.000
And then they put me in the white cell block.

01:21:29.000 --> 01:21:40.000
So I went into the white block and across a wire screen and across on the other side were the prisoners in the jail who were African-American, the males.

01:21:40.000 --> 01:21:43.000
