01:21:43.000 --> 01:21:47.000
And including Bruce Gordon, who had been thrown in.

01:21:47.000 --> 01:21:50.000
Also, he'd been picked up on one of these things.

01:21:50.000 --> 01:22:01.000
So I'm there and coming into the jail where I wasn't quite sure what would happen but I had a pretty good idea.

01:22:02.000 --> 01:22:10.000
Because I'm in there and there are put and fellows in there who pick up on car, you know, on car theory, drunk driving.

01:22:10.000 --> 01:22:13.000
Very busy there, late Friday night, Saturday.

01:22:13.000 --> 01:22:18.000
And the ass.

01:22:18.000 --> 01:22:25.000
And I was in fairly good shape.

