I, I don't know, did not know then what I know now.

01:35:28.000 --> 01:35:32.000
I was cautious, polite, and, uh, careful.

01:35:32.000 --> 01:35:34.000
It turned out it was fine, they were both terrific.

01:35:34.000 --> 01:35:41.000
When, um, the, uh, it turned out that when, um,

01:35:41.000 --> 01:35:43.000
Aaron Buchsbaum came and it represented me,

