And, he said, got it.

01:35:57.000 --> 01:36:03.000
Plus, it's a nice thing, but, so, uh, the, um,

01:36:03.000 --> 01:36:06.000
not a ring one more time, then it'll stop.

01:36:06.000 --> 01:36:07.000
I meant to turn it off.

01:36:07.000 --> 01:36:11.000
And then, um, uh, so I know he was now engaged,

