but who is this guy?

01:38:13.000 --> 01:38:15.000
And it's starting to develop.

01:38:15.000 --> 01:38:19.000
So dad calls Bruce Corwin (Metropolitan Theatres CEO) + Sherrill Corwin Sr.

01:38:19.000 --> 01:38:23.000
There's kind of a collective phone call going on here.

