And Stanley Mosk is the Attorney General, Edmund G. "Pat" Brown Sr was governor,

01:38:50.000 --> 01:38:54.000
Stanley Mosk with Attorney General California.

01:38:54.000 --> 01:39:01.000
And on there, say so, Stanley Mosk writes a letter to the Attorney General

01:39:01.000 --> 01:39:09.000
of Georgia called the Solicitor General, which says to the Attorney General

01:39:09.000 --> 01:39:12.000
of Georgia, copy to the Atlanta Constitution.

01:39:12.000 --> 01:39:14.000
Rick Tuttle is not a communist.

01:39:14.000 --> 01:39:15.000
I've known him.

01:39:15.000 --> 01:39:19.000
I have family friends who've known him since he was in a fraternity together.

01:39:19.000 --> 01:39:23.000
You may not agree on what he's doing in terms of promoting integration.

01:39:23.000 --> 01:39:28.000
So he writes, I do, but this man is no communist.

01:39:28.000 --> 01:39:30.000
Young man is no communist.

01:39:30.000 --> 01:39:35.000
He is a, and so on, and so forth.

01:39:35.000 --> 01:39:45.000
And the, and the, but another thing happened.

