My mother called her girlfriend.

01:39:47.000 --> 01:39:50.000
Her girlfriend, and she had been married the same summer.

01:39:50.000 --> 01:39:56.000
She, to my, my mother to my father, down in Arkansas.

01:39:56.000 --> 01:40:02.000
And my, and this lady had married a man named Frank Cherry, Frank Cherry.

01:40:02.000 --> 01:40:10.000
Frank Cherry went on to become governor of Arkansas before (Orval) Faubus and so on.

01:40:10.000 --> 01:40:15.000
He then, he was a Truman loyalist against the Strom Thurmond,

