you know, in the Strom Thurmond.

01:40:17.000 --> 01:40:20.000
I was a big dividing line in the South.

01:40:20.000 --> 01:40:26.000
He was appointed head of the subversive activities control board of the United States.

01:40:26.000 --> 01:40:31.000
And he called the publisher and said knock it off.

